{
    "title": "Customer Onboarding - Best Practice",
    "description": "Comprehensive customer onboarding playbook with 6 phases: Pre-Onboarding, Kickoff & Discovery, Technical Implementation, Training & Enablement, Go-Live & Hypercare, and Steady State. Includes embedded questions, exit criteria, and automation triggers.",
    "version": 1,
    "channel_name_template": "onboarding-<name>",
    "message_on_join_enabled": true,
    "message_on_join": "Welcome to the **Customer Onboarding** channel!\n\nThis channel was created as part of the Customer Onboarding playbook. All discussions, updates, and decisions related to this customer's onboarding will happen here.\n\n**Key Resources:**\n- Success Plan: [Link to be added]\n- Technical Requirements: [Link to be added]\n- Training Schedule: [Link to be added]\n\n**Team:**\n- CS Manager: @[to be assigned]\n- Implementation: @[to be assigned]\n- Training: @[to be assigned]",
    "run_summary_template_enabled": true,
    "run_summary_template": "**Customer:** \n**Segment:** (Self-serve / Scaled / High-touch / Strategic)\n**ARR:** $\n**Contract Start:** \n**Target Go-Live:** \n\n**Success Criteria:**\n- Primary Metric: \n- Target Value: \n\n**Key Stakeholders:**\n- Executive Sponsor: \n- Project Lead: \n- Technical Lead: \n\n**Current Phase:** \n**Health Score:** (Green/Yellow/Red)",
    "status_update_enabled": true,
    "reminder_timer_default_seconds": 604800,
    "retrospective_enabled": true,
    "retrospective_reminder_interval_seconds": 604800,
    "retrospective_template": "### Onboarding Summary\nBrief overview of the customer onboarding journey - what went well, what was challenging, and key outcomes achieved.\n\n### Time-to-Value Achieved\n- Time-to-First-Value: ___ days (target: <14)\n- Time-to-Go-Live: ___ days\n- Training Completion: ___% (target: >85%)\n\n### What Went Well\n- What worked that we should repeat?\n- What made this customer successful?\n- What automation saved time?\n\n### What Could Be Improved\n- Where did we struggle?\n- What took longer than expected?\n- What did the customer find frustrating?\n\n### Customer Feedback\n- Go-Live CSAT: ___/5\n- Day 90 NPS: ___\n- Key quotes from customer:\n\n### Process Improvements\n- Changes to make to this playbook:\n- New resources needed:\n- Training improvements:\n\n### Follow-up Actions\nList action items with owners and due dates to implement learnings.",
    "signal_any_keywords_enabled": true,
    "signal_any_keywords": [
        "new customer",
        "customer onboarding",
        "kickoff call",
        "go-live"
    ],
    "metrics": [],
    "checklists": [
        {
            "title": "Phase 0: Pre-Onboarding - Sales Handoff",
            "items": [
                {"title": "Customer Profile: Company name, industry, size, geography documented"},
                {"title": "ARR and contract length recorded"},
                {"title": "Segment identified (Self-serve / Scaled / High-touch / Strategic)"},
                {"title": "Contract start date confirmed"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: Why did they buy? (Business problem solved)"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: Why now? (Trigger event)"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: Why us? (Differentiator that won)"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: Who did they evaluate? (Competitors)"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: What did we promise? (Commitments made)"},
                {"title": "QUESTION: What concerns remain? (Unresolved objections)"},
                {"title": "Executive Sponsor identified with contact info"},
                {"title": "Project Lead identified with contact info"},
                {"title": "Technical Lead identified with contact info"},
                {"title": "Change Champion identified"},
                {"title": "Primary success metric defined and quantified"},
                {"title": "Target timeline documented"},
                {"title": "Current tech stack documented"},
                {"title": "Integration requirements listed"},
                {"title": "Data migration scope assessed"},
                {"title": "Security requirements identified (SSO, compliance)"},
                {"title": "Timeline risks identified"},
                {"title": "Resource risks identified"},
                {"title": "Technical risks identified"},
                {"title": "Handoff meeting completed (Sales + CS)"},
                {"title": "Customer channel created"},
                {"title": "Welcome email sent to customer"},
                {"title": "EXIT: Handoff document 100% complete"},
                {"title": "EXIT: CSM assigned and accepted"},
                {"title": "EXIT: Kickoff meeting scheduled"}
            ]
        },
        {
